data.description: Amazing opportunity to live in Evergreen Estates. Lovingly maintained and beautifully updated, this 5 bedroom / 3 full bathroom home features over $100K in upgrades, including a private pool! Updated flooring throughout the home (no carpet!), granite countertops, upgraded water features, light fixtures, and so much more. The freshly painted interior is light and bright with soaring ceilings and tons of natural light. There's something for everyone in the fully fenced, level back yard. Relax on your back deck overlooking the pool, play a game of hoops or hang out by the fire pit. All new windows on the front of the home and new HVAC (replaced 2022) for a more energy efficient home and lower utility bills. 2 car garage, NO HOA. Great location - close to shopping, dining, & schools. This is a one owner, well-loved home and it shows! Welcome Home!
